Haras Trifecta Wine Gift Set
List.Description:
A collaboration between the Antinori family of Tuscany and the Matte family of Chile, Haras de Pirque has become well known for producing exceptional wines that have earned worldwide acclaim. The Trifecta gift trio exemplifies the character and elegance of today’s Chilean wine. You've picked a winner with this Trifecta.

Wine Gift Trio Includes:

  • Haras Character
    The distinctive flavors of Haras Character Cabernet Sauvignon/Carmenere blend with notes of tobacco, earth and minerality for an elegant style that is well-balanced with astounding length. This wine has all the character for which Haras and the Maipo Valley have become known.

  • Haras Elegance
    Charming and elegant, the name paints an accurate picture of this stunning Cabernet. With a rich, full mouth-feel, the elegance of the tannins integrates well with the dark, complex flavors of this wine.

  • Haras Albis
    Made of Cabernet Sauvignon and Carmenere, the Haras Albis has complex, full-bodied flavors that exhibit flavors of black fruit, chocolate and mineral notes. Albis, as the label illustrates, signifies the dawning of a new day in winemaking, the best of old-world and new-world styles.

  • Printed insert that describes the featured wines

    Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.

Schott Zwiesel Audience - Set of 6 Champagne Flutes
List.Description:
German glass-maker Schott Zwiesel boasts a 130-year-history of innovation and success, including such break-throughs as the first machine-made stemware and the first lead-free crystal glass. They’ve once again revolutionized the industry, with the introduction Tritan Crystal glassware, which is made with titanium and zirconium instead of lead. Rigorous laboratory testing has proven the brilliance, dishwasher safety, and break-resistance of Tritan. These glasses are not only break-, scratch- and chip- resistant, but also beautiful.

The Schott Zwiesel Audience line are glasses for all occasions. A generous average of internal diameter provides an optimal surface are so that wines can develop their bouquet. Thanks to a slender mouth the aromas are precisely focused on the opening. A flowing profile and stable proportions make the glass an aesthetic experience with outstanding suitability for daily use.

The Schott Zwiesel Audience Champagne Flutes are meant for champagnes and sparkling wines.

Made in Germany. Dishwasher safe. Each flute stands 8.4in and holds 8.4oz. Boxed set of 6.
